title: It’s Facebook versus Google in lawsuit accusing search engine of gaming results
text: It’s Facebook versus Google in lawsuit accusing search engine of gaming results Tuesday, 1 September 2015 (18 minutes ago) They're two of the biggest tech companies, so there's naturally competition between Google and Facebook. But things are getting nasty in India, where Google is being accused of gaming search results, and Facebook is testifying against them.
